1
00:00:05,005 --> 00:00:09,634
(Mari (Matsuri)) If you become the governor of Tokyo, you will be nominated as vice governor.

2
00:00:09,718 --> 00:00:12,595
I'm desperate I don't want to lose you

3
00:00:12,679 --> 00:00:14,305
(Toshiko) Starting tomorrow, you will be my mom.

4
00:00:14,389 --> 00:00:17,892
I have to forget it, so I'll paste it here.

5
00:00:17,976 --> 00:00:19,811
(Akari) That's how we talked.

6
00:00:19,894 --> 00:00:21,938
I don't think I remember it anymore.

7
00:00:22,022 --> 00:00:24,065
(Takebayashi) I would like to start with the conclusion.

8
00:00:24,149 --> 00:00:26,568
Based on the property management rights of adult guardians

9
00:00:26,651 --> 00:00:29,362
‎Kamoi‎Residence and store owned by Toshiko

10
00:00:29,446 --> 00:00:33,408
We will apply to the family court for the sale of Snack Toshiko.

11
00:00:33,491 --> 00:00:34,325
(Akari) Huh?

12
00:00:34,409 --> 00:00:36,703
(Takebayashi) The decision to approve the sale will be made in about two weeks...

13
00:00:36,786 --> 00:00:38,163
Please wait a moment

14
00:00:38,246 --> 00:00:39,789
(Mari) What is the basis?

15
00:00:40,582 --> 00:00:43,710
‎The basis for arriving at the conclusion that the sale is being filed.

16
00:00:43,793 --> 00:00:45,503
‎Can I ask you something?

17
00:00:45,587 --> 00:00:50,008
I understand that you, as the guardian of an adult, have the authority to do so.

18
00:00:50,091 --> 00:00:52,469
However, currently Akari Tsukioka is

19
00:00:52,552 --> 00:00:55,722
I make a living as an employee of this store.

20
00:00:55,805 --> 00:00:58,433
Taking your job away without a justifiable reason

21
00:00:58,516 --> 00:00:59,726
‎Possibility of unfair dismissal...

22
00:00:59,809 --> 00:01:03,021
(Takebayashi) Excuse me, but this is a matter related to Mr. Tsukioka's privacy.

23
00:01:03,104 --> 00:01:05,273
‎I'm okay

24
00:01:11,738 --> 00:01:14,157
‎I apologize for the inconvenience.

25
00:01:14,240 --> 00:01:16,034
‎The amount of remuneration for an adult guardian is

26
00:01:16,117 --> 00:01:20,121
The ward's deposits and savings and current assets are used as a guide.

27
00:01:21,039 --> 00:01:24,959
In other words, if the ward's savings increase due to the sale of real estate,

28
00:01:25,043 --> 00:01:26,836
‎The amount of compensation will also increase.

29
00:01:26,920 --> 00:01:30,757
Additional fees may also be incurred when disposing of real estate.

30
00:01:31,549 --> 00:01:34,052
I'm not saying that you are.

31
00:01:34,135 --> 00:01:38,431
Just for such a purpose and without any legitimate basis.

32
00:01:38,515 --> 00:01:42,560
‎Filing a petition to sell real estate ‎If there is an adult guardian...

33
00:01:42,644 --> 00:01:47,190
I think it's only a small percentage, but it's true that it's a problem.

34
00:01:48,316 --> 00:01:52,403
Mr. Takebayashi, could you please tell us the basis?

35
00:01:55,198 --> 00:01:57,784
‎(Bamboo Forest) April 2026 now

36
00:01:57,867 --> 00:02:00,203
Toshiko Kamoi's monthly expenses are

37
00:02:00,286 --> 00:02:04,958
‎Group Home Soyokaze no Sato ‎Rent: Food, Water, Utilities: 125,000

38
00:02:05,041 --> 00:02:08,503
‎Nursing expenses 25,000 yen, total 150,000 yen

39
00:02:08,586 --> 00:02:11,172
‎The difference from the pension amount is minus 80,000 yen.

40
00:02:11,256 --> 00:02:14,259
The amount has been compensated by a transfer from Akari Tsukioka.

41
00:02:14,342 --> 00:02:15,885
(Akari) With that promise...

42
00:02:15,969 --> 00:02:19,514
I will pay the difference between the group home and pension.

43
00:02:19,597 --> 00:02:20,974
(Takebayashi) Not Tsukioka-san.

44
00:02:21,057 --> 00:02:24,769
It's just that Toshiko's snack will be paid from sales.

45
00:02:25,436 --> 00:02:28,731
I checked here and there are quite a few months in the red.

46
00:02:28,815 --> 00:02:30,692
‎Compensation and payment of utility charges

47
00:02:30,775 --> 00:02:34,070
Funded by a transfer from Akari Tsukioka

48
00:02:36,656 --> 00:02:39,367
In addition, Toshiko Kamoi is under contract.

49
00:02:39,450 --> 00:02:41,786
‎Payment to the guarantor company‎Mr. Tsukioka

50
00:02:41,870 --> 00:02:44,122
Guarantee company?

51
00:02:44,747 --> 00:02:47,625
Did the group home request a guarantor?

52
00:02:48,585 --> 00:02:50,920
‎If you aren't there, you won't be able to enter.

53
00:02:51,004 --> 00:02:53,798
I wish I could be

54
00:02:53,882 --> 00:02:57,051
‎It seems to be difficult without family.

55
00:02:57,135 --> 00:02:59,345
‎Not a blood relative ‎No obligation to do so⸺

56
00:02:59,429 --> 00:03:02,849
The current situation is that the payment by Mr. Tsukioka is barely making it through.

57
00:03:02,932 --> 00:03:05,602
In the unlikely event that Mr. Tsukioka no longer has the will to pay...

58
00:03:05,685 --> 00:03:07,353
It won't go away

59
00:03:07,979 --> 00:03:09,105
‎That's not it

60
00:03:09,188 --> 00:03:11,649
(Bamboo forest) Also, in case of illness or accident,

61
00:03:11,733 --> 00:03:13,276
‎In case of insolvency

62
00:03:13,359 --> 00:03:16,404
Furthermore, due to Toshiko Kamoi's own illness, etc.

63
00:03:16,487 --> 00:03:19,282
If you incur a large amount of expenses, you will immediately go bankrupt...

64
00:03:19,365 --> 00:03:21,784
I'll do something, even if it means borrowing money.

65
00:03:21,868 --> 00:03:23,745
‎It's okay to talk about your feelings.

66
00:03:24,954 --> 00:03:28,333
I have a duty to protect the rights and lives of my wards.

67
00:03:28,416 --> 00:03:31,544
You cannot build on something unstable and uncertain.

68
00:03:31,628 --> 00:03:34,422
Unstable and uncertain...

69
00:03:35,506 --> 00:03:37,342
‎Do you mean my feelings?

70
00:03:37,425 --> 00:03:38,426
‎Not just for you

71
00:03:38,509 --> 00:03:40,386
But here...

72
00:03:40,470 --> 00:03:42,305
‎Snack Toshiko

73
00:03:42,388 --> 00:03:47,393
Mom... This is Toshiko's precious place.

74
00:03:47,477 --> 00:03:48,603
I was appointed

75
00:03:48,686 --> 00:03:51,147
(Takebayashi) Procedures for business transfer have not been carried out, right?

76
00:03:55,318 --> 00:03:57,654
‎What are Toshiko Kamoi's intentions?

77
00:04:01,115 --> 00:04:04,994
An adult guardian is a guardian of a person who is found to have insufficient judgment.

78
00:04:05,078 --> 00:04:08,915
Ability to conclude contracts for property management and personal custody

79
00:04:08,998 --> 00:04:12,794
That's why we must fully assess the ward's intentions.

80
00:04:12,877 --> 00:04:14,921
‎You need to scoop it out, right?

81
00:04:15,004 --> 00:04:16,923
‎Guidelines formulated by the Ministry of Health, Labor and Welfare, etc.

82
00:04:17,006 --> 00:04:18,091
Of course I know

83
00:04:18,925 --> 00:04:22,387
So why in the process of considering a sale?

84
00:04:22,470 --> 00:04:25,598
Didn't you ask Tsukioka-san's opinion?

85
00:04:27,225 --> 00:04:29,769
‎Mr. Tsukioka for 10 years

86
00:04:29,852 --> 00:04:32,897
‎I run this shop with Toshiko Kamoi.

87
00:04:32,981 --> 00:04:35,858
They have built a relationship that is like family.

88
00:04:35,942 --> 00:04:38,069
‎What is Mr. Tsukioka's opinion?

89
00:04:38,152 --> 00:04:40,530
In estimating Toshiko Kamoi's intentions

90
00:04:40,613 --> 00:04:43,366
‎This could be very useful information.

91
00:04:44,409 --> 00:04:48,329
‎Intention is “feeling”, right?

92
00:04:48,871 --> 00:04:50,915
You just cut me off in one fell swoop.

93
00:04:50,999 --> 00:04:52,542
‎As you say

94
00:04:52,625 --> 00:04:54,544
‎-(Mari) Then... ‎-(Takebayashi) What I should guess is⸺

95
00:04:54,627 --> 00:04:57,964
This is Toshiko Kamoi's feelings, not Tsukioka's.

96
00:04:58,047 --> 00:04:59,507
‎Of course, so...

97
00:04:59,590 --> 00:05:01,175
(Takebayashi) As I said earlier,

98
00:05:01,259 --> 00:05:03,469
Feelings are unstable and uncertain

99
00:05:03,553 --> 00:05:06,347
What's important is how you feel right now.

100
00:05:08,016 --> 00:05:11,811
‎I was with you‎Not before the onset of dementia

101
00:05:12,854 --> 00:05:14,355
(Mari) Sale of real estate

102
00:05:14,439 --> 00:05:17,442
What is Toshiko Kamoi's current intention?

103
00:05:17,525 --> 00:05:19,569
That's how I perceived it

104
00:05:19,652 --> 00:05:20,570
‎What is the basis?

105
00:05:20,653 --> 00:05:22,363
‎Interview with the person in question

106
00:05:22,447 --> 00:05:25,491
‎Hearing from the care manager and staff of the group home.

107
00:05:25,575 --> 00:05:30,621
To those who are currently in close contact with Toshiko Kamoi

108
00:05:31,372 --> 00:05:34,625
In addition, the current management status of Snack Toshiko

109
00:05:34,709 --> 00:05:36,919
‎Toshiko Kamoi’s asset status

110
00:05:37,003 --> 00:05:39,255
‎Considering expected future expenses, etc.

111
00:05:39,339 --> 00:05:40,882
‎Sale of real estate

112
00:05:40,965 --> 00:05:44,343
We have decided that it is best to secure funding.

113
00:05:45,636 --> 00:05:49,432
There's more to do, so it's time

114
00:05:51,184 --> 00:05:52,935
‎How much...

115
00:05:54,562 --> 00:05:57,982
How much money would I have to avoid having to sell this place?

116
00:05:58,066 --> 00:06:01,277
At least as of now, Mr. Tsukioka is being paid.

117
00:06:01,360 --> 00:06:04,906
Difference between monthly group home usage fee and pension: 80,000 yen

118
00:06:04,989 --> 00:06:07,367
‎3500 yen to the guarantor company

119
00:06:07,450 --> 00:06:10,578
‎Total of 83,500 yen for 10 years

120
00:06:11,120 --> 00:06:12,663
‎10.02 million yen...

121
00:06:16,667 --> 00:06:18,795
The application to the family court will be filed at the beginning of next week, right?

122
00:06:18,878 --> 00:06:19,837
‎Yes

123
00:06:19,921 --> 00:06:23,299
‎If by then ‎I have a prospect of securing funding.

124
00:06:23,382 --> 00:06:26,844
If I could present it to you, would you please reconsider?

125
00:06:26,928 --> 00:06:29,222
‎We will consider it.

126
00:06:33,684 --> 00:06:35,686
‎The story about Taraba is meaningless.

127
00:06:36,396 --> 00:06:38,856
‎If you have such strong feelings

128
00:06:38,940 --> 00:06:40,191
‎Why in the early stages of dementia?

129
00:06:40,274 --> 00:06:42,944
Did you not complete the procedures for business transfer?

130
00:06:44,362 --> 00:06:45,404
‎At that point

131
00:06:45,488 --> 00:06:48,658
You could have become a voluntary guardian.

132
00:06:49,242 --> 00:06:50,201
(Akari) Eh...

133
00:06:50,284 --> 00:06:52,495
Wasn't it suggested at the (Takebayashi) Comprehensive Support Center?

134
00:06:56,457 --> 00:06:59,669
‎It's too late‎If your judgment ability is insufficient⸺

135
00:06:59,752 --> 00:07:02,547
After the family court's judgment is handed down

136
00:07:03,297 --> 00:07:04,382
‎That's how you say it...

137
00:07:05,591 --> 00:07:07,343
(Takebayashi) We look forward to hearing from you.

138
00:07:15,476 --> 00:07:16,727
(sound of door closing)

139
00:07:18,020 --> 00:07:20,940
Sorry for being so embarrassing, hehe...

140
00:07:21,023 --> 00:07:23,442
(Mari) I'm not embarrassed at all.

141
00:07:27,029 --> 00:07:30,283
Thank you for being so reassuring

142
00:07:31,617 --> 00:07:34,912
‎(Mari) ‎I'm sorry for not being able to overturn it here.

143
00:07:34,996 --> 00:07:36,330
‎Yeah

144
00:07:38,374 --> 00:07:40,585
‎Zuhoshi I was stabbed.

145
00:07:41,836 --> 00:07:46,048
It's still okay It's still okay I came here on a makeshift basis

146
00:07:46,716 --> 00:07:50,303
‎About the store ‎About Toshiko's mom

147
00:07:51,679 --> 00:07:52,597
(Akari) What happened?

148
00:07:52,680 --> 00:07:55,850
(Toshiko) Ah... no, it's fine after all.

149
00:07:55,933 --> 00:07:57,185
‎No, it's different, it's weird

150
00:07:57,268 --> 00:07:59,478
Ah, not at all, I don't feel like that at all.

151
00:07:59,562 --> 00:08:00,730
‎I don't agree

152
00:08:02,315 --> 00:08:05,276
(Mari) But it's hard, isn't it?

153
00:08:05,860 --> 00:08:07,320
It's still okay though

154
00:08:07,403 --> 00:08:10,114
Preparing for when things aren't okay

155
00:08:11,616 --> 00:08:13,534
It was the same with my mother.

156
00:08:13,618 --> 00:08:14,869
I'm still alive

157
00:08:14,952 --> 00:08:17,288
I have to prepare for what happens after I die.

158
00:08:18,581 --> 00:08:20,291
‎The system is for people.

159
00:08:20,374 --> 00:08:25,213
We need to change the current situation where we tend to ignore the feelings that make people human.

160
00:08:26,964 --> 00:08:28,674
‎That's amazing, Mari-chan

161
00:08:28,758 --> 00:08:30,009
‎No, that's it...

162
00:08:30,092 --> 00:08:33,888
‎I was surprised just now‎Mr. Takebayashi.

163
00:08:33,971 --> 00:08:35,765
‎You remembered yesterday.

164
00:08:36,515 --> 00:08:38,059
‎Just by looking at my business card

165
00:08:39,435 --> 00:08:41,229
‎It's an ingrained fragility.

166
00:08:41,312 --> 00:08:42,438
‎Huh?

167
00:08:43,105 --> 00:08:47,193
It is said that calling your name increases the success rate of negotiations and business negotiations.

168
00:08:47,276 --> 00:08:48,819
It's called the name calling effect.

169
00:08:48,903 --> 00:08:50,571
‎Wow~

170
00:08:52,114 --> 00:08:55,368
‎I see, that makes me happy.

171
00:08:56,244 --> 00:08:57,078
‎Huh?

172
00:08:57,828 --> 00:09:01,582
‎Your name will be remembered ‎You will call me.

173
00:09:01,666 --> 00:09:05,586
‎But it means that you are using it.

174
00:09:07,338 --> 00:09:09,966
‎That kind of... happy feeling

175
00:09:10,549 --> 00:09:12,134
‎For one's own benefit

176
00:09:13,511 --> 00:09:14,804
It's not me

177
00:09:15,554 --> 00:09:16,389
‎Huh?

178
00:09:16,472 --> 00:09:18,140
It's for me, right?

179
00:09:19,976 --> 00:09:21,727
Thank you, Mari-chan

180
00:09:24,146 --> 00:09:27,483
‎Um, here‎Sales are suddenly declining.

181
00:09:27,567 --> 00:09:30,278
About 5 minutes walk away

182
00:09:30,361 --> 00:09:33,406
There was a metal factory on Samejima.

183
00:09:33,990 --> 00:09:38,286
Last August, I moved to Shizuoka.

184
00:09:38,953 --> 00:09:39,954
‎Huh?

185
00:09:40,037 --> 00:09:43,332
‎Regular customers‎Most of them were from there.

186
00:09:44,333 --> 00:09:48,212
‎Acchanga‎He brought people from the neighborhood.

187
00:09:48,296 --> 00:09:49,505
‎Save money

188
00:09:50,798 --> 00:09:54,385
I even raised the price little by little.

189
00:09:56,512 --> 00:09:58,806
‎I can't get excited for a while

190
00:09:59,473 --> 00:10:00,850
‎My lack of strength

191
00:10:01,767 --> 00:10:06,522
‎No, it is caused by external factors ‎Changes in the structural environment

192
00:10:06,605 --> 00:10:08,399
It's not my fault

193
00:10:08,482 --> 00:10:09,317
‎Huh?

194
00:10:10,026 --> 00:10:13,779
The reason for the decrease in sales is clear and force majeure.

195
00:10:13,863 --> 00:10:17,992
You may be eligible for some kind of subsidy or grant.

196
00:10:18,075 --> 00:10:20,786
‎Contact your acquaintances at the Ministry of Health, Labor and Welfare and the Ministry of Economy, Trade and Industry.

197
00:10:20,870 --> 00:10:23,456
Ask if there's anything you'd like to target...

198
00:10:24,165 --> 00:10:25,916
(Shizukuishi) You have built up so far.

199
00:10:26,000 --> 00:10:28,794
‎Achievement Networks Trust Backing

200
00:10:28,878 --> 00:10:32,298
All of that depends on your father's presence.

201
00:10:34,216 --> 00:10:35,384
I'll look into it

202
00:10:36,177 --> 00:10:38,888
‎First of all, if you can make a goal

203
00:10:39,472 --> 00:10:43,476
Then, guarantor company payment: 3,500 yen per month

204
00:10:43,559 --> 00:10:45,186
‎This shouldn't be necessary.

205
00:10:45,269 --> 00:10:47,313
‎Eh! but…

206
00:10:47,396 --> 00:10:48,731
(Mari) Elderly care facility

207
00:10:48,814 --> 00:10:53,361
Refusal to move in solely on the basis of not having a guarantor is inappropriate.

208
00:10:53,444 --> 00:10:55,446
‎As it is also in the notification of the Ministry of Health, Labor and Welfare.

209
00:10:55,529 --> 00:10:56,822
Is that so?

210
00:10:57,740 --> 00:10:58,741
Ah, I'll go in a bit.

211
00:10:58,824 --> 00:11:00,618
(Akari) Huh? Mari-chan?

212
00:11:01,369 --> 00:11:06,082
‎♪～

213
00:11:57,550 --> 00:12:01,345
‎～♪

214
00:12:02,596 --> 00:12:04,473
(Facility Director) Of course I know.

215
00:12:04,557 --> 00:12:09,186
But there is still no system in place to comply with the notice.

216
00:12:09,270 --> 00:12:10,938
‎What do you mean?

217
00:12:11,522 --> 00:12:15,818
(Facility Director) For example, Toshiko became ill.

218
00:12:15,901 --> 00:12:21,699
When you are forced to choose a treatment option without being able to confirm your intentions

219
00:12:21,782 --> 00:12:27,455
When you reach level 4 or 5 of nursing care and need to move from one facility to another

220
00:12:27,538 --> 00:12:31,876
It's hard to tell, but when he passed away.

221
00:12:31,959 --> 00:12:34,795
We are unable to respond.

222
00:12:34,879 --> 00:12:37,131
‎Adult guardianship is for that purpose...

223
00:12:37,214 --> 00:12:42,261
An adult guardian is only a representative of the individual.

224
00:12:42,344 --> 00:12:45,431
The person in question cannot be the person's guarantor.

225
00:12:45,514 --> 00:12:48,309
The same applies to adult guardians.

226
00:12:48,392 --> 00:12:50,895
‎To make the facility capable of handling

227
00:12:50,978 --> 00:12:55,524
It is necessary to increase the number of qualified personnel and prepare equipment.

228
00:12:55,608 --> 00:12:58,402
Therefore, if usage fees are to increase

229
00:12:58,486 --> 00:13:02,239
There may be some people who have no choice but to move out.

230
00:13:03,032 --> 00:13:06,202
‎I want to say that we too

231
00:13:06,285 --> 00:13:08,454
‎For any situation

232
00:13:08,537 --> 00:13:11,123
“Welcome, come, don’t worry about anything”

233
00:13:14,752 --> 00:13:16,170
‎I was uneducated

234
00:13:16,253 --> 00:13:19,965
Thank you very much for taking time out of your busy schedule to talk to us.

235
00:13:26,138 --> 00:13:28,766
(Workers' excited voices) ‎(Female) ‎Huh? Is there such a thing?

236
00:13:28,766 --> 00:13:28,849
(The excited voices of the workers)

237
00:13:28,849 --> 00:13:31,268
(Workers' excited voices) ‎(Igarashi) ‎Subsidy up to 200,000 yen will be given...

238
00:13:32,645 --> 00:13:34,647
(Igarashi) It's noisy! (voice becomes quieter)

239
00:13:34,730 --> 00:13:36,106
(Igarashi clicks his tongue)

240
00:13:36,190 --> 00:13:37,316
‎Sorry

241
00:13:37,399 --> 00:13:39,318
‎Dene Handrail Elimination of steps‎Repair of bath and toilet

242
00:13:39,318 --> 00:13:40,945
(Caster) Play the role of steering the Tokyo government. Handrails Eliminate steps. Repair baths and toilets.

243
00:13:40,945 --> 00:13:41,028
‎Dene Handrail Elimination of steps‎Repair of bath and toilet

244
00:13:41,028 --> 00:13:41,612
The second place to entrust it to is here‎Removal of handrails and steps‎Repair of bath and toilet

245
00:13:41,612 --> 00:13:41,695
Here is the second place to entrust it to.

246
